	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)">Mark<add>&#63;</add> <date>October 23<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1849</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dr. Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed please find<lb/> &#35;3 for the Occident from <date>Rosh Hashana 1849</date><lb/> to <date>1850</date>. wishing that you may find a great<lb/> number of subscribers more for your valuable<lb/> publication&#44; and hoping that <add>your</add> calls on the<lb/> different Congregations in the <placeName>United States</placeName><lb/> to meet in <placeName>New York</placeName> may be of success to<lb/> raise a standard to our religion&#44; and to<lb/> provide for the education of our <sic>offsprings</sic><lb/> in our faith</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">I Remain dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">very respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">L. Leopold</persName></p>
				<p>P. S.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">You will also find enclosed<lb/> &#36;2. which you will please to hand as a<lb/> donation&#44; to the Messengers for our suffering<lb/> brothers at <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName></p>
		</body>
